<div class="story">  <p>Ocean Winds is a condominium complex in Kitty Hawk situated high up on a hill which offers some ocean views off in the distance for a few of the units. There are 26 units, each with 2 bedrooms and one full bath, contained in 5 separate buildings. Ocean Winds condos are located On Kitty Hawk Rd just south of the community of <a href="https://www.outerbankshome.com/outer banks/real estate/KittyHawk/ted-wood-kitty-hawk-terrace.asp" title="Ted Wood Kitty Hawk Terrace">Ted Wood Kitty Hawk Terrace</a> and north of the subdivision of <a href="https://www.outerbankshome.com/outer banks/real estate/KittyHawk/woodard-acres.asp" title="Woodard Acres">Woodard Acres</a>. </p> 
